  "texts": [
    "Then, the groundtruth spots were matched one-to-one to the decoded spots if the barcodes were identical and the centroids were closer than 6 pixels.",
    "Sensitivity is defined as the fraction of groundtruth spots matched with a decoded spot.",
    "Specificity is defined as the fraction of matched decoded spots over all decoded spots.",
    "Empty rate is the fraction of empty barcodes among all decoded barcodes and is inversely related to specificity.",
    "Nature Communications | (2024) 15:2511"
